{"sections":{"image_with_text_overlay_wF9cJP":{"type":"image-with-text-overlay","blocks":{"subheading_jmw47P":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":""}},"heading_HU4TJb":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Returns Guide","heading_max_width":15,"title_size":72,"title_size_mobile":20,"use_h1":true}},"text_8nUtzF":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p>Follow our step-by-step guide to making a return<\/p>","enlarge_text":true}}},"block_order":["subheading_jmw47P","heading_HU4TJb","text_8nUtzF"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/","height":"adapt","height_desktop":300,"height_mobile":120,"image_link":"","full_width":true,"text_alignment":"center center","mobile_overlay_under":false,"overlay_style":"full image-overlay--bg-shadow"}},"rich_text_xYHxUX":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_GcfAjR":{"type":"heading","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Request a Return","use_h1":false}},"text_m7xMFX":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Start by emailing us at<a href=\"mailto:support@drinkllc.com\">support@drinkllc.com<\/a>with your order number. Our team responds within 1 business day and will send a prepaid return label if your item meets the policy.”<\/p>","enlarge_text":true}}},"block_order":["heading_GcfAjR","text_m7xMFX"],"settings":{"height":"medium","text_alignment":"center","full_width":false,"color_scheme":"default"}},"main":{"type":"main-page","settings":{"show_page_title":false,"full_width":false}},"image_with_text_EWRmm6":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_bwNNXe":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Prepare Your Bike","use_h1":false}},"text_mkPBj9":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Repack the bike in its original box with everything it came with — charger, keys, tools, and manuals. To protect the bike in shipping, the front wheel must be boxed separately from the frame.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_bwNNXe","text_mkPBj9"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Tunathemechanic.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"2"}},"image_with_text_zK74RN":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_d7Adz7":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Confirm with Drink LLC","use_h1":true}},"text_DRgW3F":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Snap a few photos of your packed box and send them to us. This quick step ensures your bike is fully protected and avoids any shipping surprises.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_d7Adz7","text_DRgW3F"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Bikeshopmulti.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"right","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"default"}},"image_with_text_89N96B":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_PtVaWc":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Ship it Back","use_h1":false}},"text_H4MMUb":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>For bikes, we’ll provide a prepaid return label so shipping is easy. For accessories, customers arrange their own shipping, just make sure it’s tracked so both of us can follow it.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_PtVaWc","text_H4MMUb"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shippingtous.png","image_width":700,"image_link":"","image_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"2"}},"rich_text_L8bDPr":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_fxyAb4":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>After we receive and inspect your return, refunds are issued to your original payment method within 5–7 business days. If your item doesn’t meet return criteria, we’ll notify you right away and give you options for next steps.<\/p>","enlarge_text":true}}},"block_order":["text_fxyAb4"],"name":"Rich text","settings":{"height":"medium","text_alignment":"center","full_width":false,"color_scheme":"default"}},"faq_header_wMhwag":{"type":"faq-header","settings":{"title":"Returns FAQs","use_h1":true,"text":"","show_search":false,"show_index":false,"index_head